  <official_title>A Randomised Phase III Study of the Efficacy of High Dose Dexamethasone Versus High Dose Dexamethasone in Combination With Rituximab (MabTheraÂ®)in Patients With Newly Diagnosed Idiopathic Thrombocytopenic Purpura (ITP)</official_title>
